## What's Still Good ✅

- Comprehensive XML documentation on all public APIs
- Multiple safety confirmations in the UI
- Clean domain model ([DiskInfo](file:///Users/pisarz/Documents/projekty/test-diskcloning/DiskCloner.Core/Models/DiskInfo.cs#8-113), [PartitionInfo](file:///Users/pisarz/Documents/projekty/test-diskcloning/DiskCloner.Core/Models/PartitionInfo.cs#8-188), [CloneOperation](file:///Users/pisarz/Documents/projekty/test-diskcloning/DiskCloner.Core/Models/CloneOperation.cs#6-70), [CloneResult](file:///Users/pisarz/Documents/projekty/test-diskcloning/DiskCloner.Core/Models/CloneOperation.cs#231-288))
- `SafeFileHandle` usage throughout native interop
- Detailed logging with timestamps
- Cancellation support via `CancellationTokenSource`
- New partition mapping adds significant correctness improvement
- Offline/online disk lifecycle is now properly handled
